  "detailed_description": "The complete bingo party game! use \"Local\" mode to host your own parties with any number of people! Just display the game on a computer, TV or projector and have all your participants play along using real bingo cards with dabbers/chips, mobile phones, etc. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1219230/extras/7d9ec1ce602a2642571b71cfdeccbe22.poster.avif?t=1715883073\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1219230/extras/7d9ec1ce602a2642571b71cfdeccbe22.webm?t=1715883073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1219230/extras/7d9ec1ce602a2642571b71cfdeccbe22.mp4?t=1715883073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Online</h2>*** Use \"Online\" mode to host a game of up to 50 people! Have all your participants go to the URL \"bigbash.games\" on any device with a browser and use the generated room code to join in! You can play sitting around your TV, projecting in a large hall, or streaming online! The perfect way to have fun with all of your friends/family during the pandemic. ***<br><br>Current Patterns:<br>1 Line, 2 Lines, 4 corners, T, X, Full card.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1219230/extras/286f27510b46f70a6240f50e766bfbc4.avif?t=1715883073\" width=478 height=270 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >That's a Bingo!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1219230/extras/055612de48caf8368f1fdbe5123cc58e.poster.avif?t=1715883073\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1219230/extras/055612de48caf8368f1fdbe5123cc58e.webm?t=1715883073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1219230/extras/055612de48caf8368f1fdbe5123cc58e.mp4?t=1715883073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "The complete bingo party game! use \"Local\" mode to host your own parties with any number of people! Just display the game on a computer, TV or projector and have all your participants play along using real bingo cards with dabbers/chips, mobile phones, etc. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1219230/extras/7d9ec1ce602a2642571b71cfdeccbe22.poster.avif?t=1715883073\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1219230/extras/7d9ec1ce602a2642571b71cfdeccbe22.webm?t=1715883073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1219230/extras/7d9ec1ce602a2642571b71cfdeccbe22.mp4?t=1715883073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Online</h2>*** Use \"Online\" mode to host a game of up to 50 people! Have all your participants go to the URL \"bigbash.games\" on any device with a browser and use the generated room code to join in! You can play sitting around your TV, projecting in a large hall, or streaming online! The perfect way to have fun with all of your friends/family during the pandemic. ***<br><br>Current Patterns:<br>1 Line, 2 Lines, 4 corners, T, X, Full card.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1219230/extras/286f27510b46f70a6240f50e766bfbc4.avif?t=1715883073\" width=478 height=270 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >That's a Bingo!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1219230/extras/055612de48caf8368f1fdbe5123cc58e.poster.avif?t=1715883073\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1219230/extras/055